      <title>Installation view of ‘Cœur sucré’, a solo exhibition by Galina Munroe. The exhib...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWQ1jXQlHVf/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/657343464_18111583219685413_4884098793112393947_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=108&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTgxOTg2Njg1ODIxODI0OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=8CavJYzC7EQQ7kNvwHMDiga&amp;_nc_oc=AdrPxplLj2umS5o29XPJzrDFQTVDxt3adpohin8OHt_CIzsWGtmvPR6rlyeHzVN1-Yk&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=imOOyRXhwYNxN0SfA4rQmQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzBkXLCNsDmRR8wAXkfJActUl2B-mlOk5KWKZ4W1MI2Qw&amp;oe=69C8F3D1" alt="Instagram billede fra @bricksgallery_cph" /></p><p><strong>@bricksgallery_cph</strong></p><p>Installation view of ‘Cœur sucré’, a solo exhibition by Galina Munroe. The exhibition continues through April 25.<br/>
<br/>
Working with simplified shapes, saturated colour, and open space, Munroe approaches intimacy as a visual language shaped by shared memory and the quiet rhythms of everyday life. The French title nods to her upbringing and sets the tone for the exhibition, emphasising softness and emotional depth.<br/>
<br/>
For inquiries, please DM or contact hello@bricksgallery.dk.<br/>
<br/>
N.B. Holiday Information:<br/>
Please note that the gallery will be closed during Easter from April 2 to April 7.<br/>
<br/>
